===============================================================================

  RailsCrawler has been installed!

  Configuration file created at: config/initializers/rails_crawler.rb

  Available rake tasks:
    rake crawler:crawl              # Crawl entire site
    rake crawler:crawl_models       # Crawl only Rails model URLs
    rake crawler:config             # Show configuration

  Environment variables:
    BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000 rake crawler:crawl
    FORMAT=json OUTPUT_FILE=report.json rake crawler:crawl
    MAX_CONCURRENT=10 rake crawler:crawl
    FOLLOW_EXTERNAL=true rake crawler:crawl

  Command line usage:
    rails_crawler http://localhost:3000
    rails_crawler --format json --output report.json http://localhost:3000

  Ruby usage:
    RailsCrawler.crawl('http://localhost:3000')
    RailsCrawler.crawl('http://localhost:3000', max_concurrent: 10)

===============================================================================